description:
Ensure all query logic handles both Manual and Awaiting fields

Affected code:
1. query.Ready() - already uses IsAwaitingHuman() helper
2. query.Apply() with Awaiting filter - needs to also check Manual
3. tk list --awaiting - needs to match Manual=true ticks
4. tk next --awaiting - needs to return Manual=true ticks

Implementation:
In filter Apply() for Awaiting:
  // Use helper that handles both fields
  awaitingType := t.GetAwaitingType()
  if filter.Awaiting != nil {
      if awaitingType != *filter.Awaiting {
          continue
      }
  }

The key is using the helper methods consistently so backwards compat is automatic.
